{
  "stem": "9156.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And every time when I think of somebody-- Rudy Levy-- L-E-V-Y.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can name them-- though, you know, we forgot names purposely-- that were Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then there were Germans like my husband, who I think has done more courageous things as an anti-Nazi than I ever did because in some ways could do it with his-- as he always said-- unfortunately blue eyes and blond hair.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is something I will say in a little while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, but he did incredible things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I give only examples.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I certainly distributed leaflets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people don't understand what that means.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It felt as if they can look through the hole, through the-- through the pocket seeing that, that you carry something, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the way you could hand them out, only shake somebody's hand and push it in their hands.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I cannot tell all the details.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It sounds like nothing in a country that has free communication.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But communication was terribly necessary because we had to let people know that there was a resistance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People think there was no resistance, but there was a resistance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, one thing I have to say is that I always say it's one of the worst things that happened in some ways, and that is that one couldn't communicate with anybody one didn't know before the time of the Nazis, which meant that there have been lots of small groups of resistance that never knew from each other.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know an awful lot today more than I knew at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just didn't know from each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't talk because you couldn't trust anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
